title: Kawaii dake ja Mono Tarinai!
original_name: カワイイだけじゃモノ足りない！
sinopse:
After Fujikawa Alice’s parents died in a plane crash, they left behind a crumbling modeling agency with a massive amount of debt. The only model in the agency is Alice. To scout the popular model “Raitou”, she slips into the audition house…?!

Source: Operation Boredom
